ROSER v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND HOUSE OF CORRECTION [App. No. 6,

September Term, 1964.]

Decided September 24, 1964.

Before Henderson, C. J., and Hammond, Prescott, Horney and Marbury, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post convic*611tion relief is denied for the reasons set out in the opinion of Judge Rutledge in the court below.

Application denied.
